This effort will mature Vulnerability Modules for Group 2-3 Unmanned Aerial Systems, Rotary Wing, and subsonic cruise missiles
to a Vulnerability Modules Readiness Level 5; Supersonic Cruise Missiles to Vulnerability Module Readiness Level 4; and



