Description: This effort develops an easily emplaced, rapidly deployable, multi-modal geophysical tactical array for persistent,
wide area, remote, non-line-of-sight monitoring for potential deep sensing to extend monitoring ranges and investigate new
processing techniques to allow for the battlespace awareness needed in Multi-Domain Operations in both Competition and Armed
Conflict phases.

FY 2025 Plans:

