Will develop initial expedient concepts to rapidly increase the level of protection of key assets from weapons effects. Will develop
survivability assessment methodologies for critical sites, functions, and personnel, accounting for various attack scenarios and the
interdependencies of components, assets, systems, and systems of systems.
