Remarks
 FY 2027 CMPC prime development contract supports continued development of micro-services and continuous software integration for advanced mission planning, execution,
 dynamic re-planning, and analysis capabilities. FY 2027 supports incremental funding for the CMPC Primary Software Development efforts awarded via a competitive contract
