air) against emerging multi- threats.
FY 2026 Plans:
Leverage outcomes in Musculoskeletal Injury (ARMI) study to validate and translate musculoskeletal injury risk and performance
degrading prediction tools, as well as strategies to optimize physical readiness to provide evidence-based recommendations for


