engage targets during reconnaissance missions. These technologies will produce a mix of fully integrated software, AI algorithms/models, and ground-based/aerial-
based drones to execute reconnaissance and engagement tasks in battlefield conditions.

 Work in this project complements Program Element (PE) 0602180A (Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Advanced Technologies) / Project CL7 (ATR Using
 Multiple Cooperative Sensors App Tech)

